    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Code implementation touching `.tsx` file. Refactors WorkspacePane to consume new shared PaneHeader + embeds the LegalWorkspace experience (load-bearing for FR-10, FR-11 and unblocks tasks 031/032/034/035). ADR-012 (shared components), ADR-021 (Fluent v9 tokens), ADR-028 (authenticatedFetch for layout fetch) all apply. FULL rigor with code-review + adr-check at Step 9.5.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>C</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Touches `WorkspacePane.tsx` — shared file with tasks 031, 032. Must serialize within group C on that file.</parallel-reason>
